BioDmela

The undirected graph BioDmela has 7393 nodes and 25569 edges.

RAM requirements

The RAM requirements for the nodes and edges data structures are 1.15MB and 78.94KB respectively.

Degree centrality

The minimum node degree is 1, the maximum node degree is 190, the mode degree is 1, the mean degree is 6.92 and the node degree median is 3.

The nodes with highest degree centrality are: 479 (degree 190), 1392 (degree 149), 731 (degree 122), 873 (degree 115) and 96 (degree 113).
